snippet.title: Pixel Survival Game 2.o - Battle Royale Arena update 1.09!
snippet.description:
Join our discord!
https://discord.gg/sMaqyBx5Cf

Pixel Survival Game 2.o is currently in BETA, available for download on Google Play App Store, Huawei App Gallery, and the Amazon App Store!

Please subscribe, follow twitter and facebook so I can deliver you the most updated news of this and other games!

Follow facebook page for up to date news @ http://www.facebook.com/cowbeans
Follow twitter for up to date news @ http://www.twitter.com/_cowbeans
